"20\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Quality Briquettes[/cmsms_heading][cmsms_text animation_delay=\"0\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Orthodontics is the branch of dentistry that corrects teeth and jaws that are positioned improperly.</p>\r\n[/cmsms_text][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_padding_bottom=\"50\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" data_bg_position=\"top center\" data_color=\"default\" data_padding_right=\"3\" data_padding_left=\"3\" data_width=\"boxed\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_padding_bottom=\"50\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" data_bg_position=\"top center\" data_color=\"default\" data_padding_right=\"3\" data_padding_left=\"3\" data_width=\"boxed\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][cmsms_sidebar sidebar=\"booking-a-visit\"][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_padding_bottom=\"50\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" data_bg_position=\"top center\" data_color=\"default\" data_padding_right=\"3\" data_padding_left=\"3\" data_width=\"boxed\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_width=\"boxed\" data_color=\"default\" data_bg_img=\"74|http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/content-dot3-1-14x300.jpg|medium\" data_bg_position=\"top center\" data_bg_repeat=\"repeat-x\" data_bg_attachment=\"fixed\" data_bg_size=\"auto\" data_bg_parallax=\"true\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_padding_bottom=\"50\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][cmsms_heading type=\"h1\" font_weight=\"normal\" font_style=\"normal\" text_align=\"left\" margin_top=\"0\" margin_bottom=\"20\" animation_delay=\"0\"][/cmsms_heading][cmsms_heading type=\"h6\" font_family=\"Open+Sans:300,300italic,400,400italic,700,700italic\" font_size=\"14\" font_weight=\"normal\" font_style=\"normal\" text_align=\"left\" color=\"#07a7e3\" margin_top=\"0\" margin_bottom=\"20\" animation_delay=\"0\"]What we do[/cmsms_heading][cmsms_heading type=\"h2\" font_size=\"26\" line_height=\"36\" font_weight=\"normal\" font_style=\"normal\" text_align=\"left\" margin_top=\"0\" margin_bottom=\"20\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Our Services[/cmsms_heading][cmsms_posts_slider orderby=\"date\" order=\"DESC\" post_type=\"project\" portfolio_categories=\"dental-care,new-services,services,special-services\" columns=\"4\" count=\"12\" pause=\"5\" portfolio_metadata=\"title,categories,comments,likes\" animation_delay=\"0\"][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_width=\"boxed\" data_padding_left=\"3\" data_padding_right=\"3\" data_color=\"default\" data_bg_position=\"top center\" data_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_padding_bottom=\"50\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_padding_bottom=\"50\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" data_bg_position=\"top center\" data_color=\"default\" data_padding_right=\"3\" data_padding_left=\"3\" data_width=\"boxed\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/2\"][cmsms_heading type=\"h1\" font_family=\"Open+Sans:300,300italic,400,400italic,700,700italic\" font_weight=\"normal\" font_style=\"normal\" text_align=\"left\" margin_top=\"0\" margin_bottom=\"20\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Testimonials[/cmsms_heading][cmsms_heading type=\"h6\" font_family=\"Open+Sans:300,300italic,400,400italic,700,700italic\" font_size=\"14\" font_weight=\"normal\" font_style=\"normal\" text_align=\"left\" color=\"#07a7e3\" margin_top=\"0\" margin_bottom=\"20\" animation_delay=\"0\"]What Our Patients Say About Us[/cmsms_heading][cmsms_quotes mode=\"slider\" type=\"box\" speed=\"5\" animation_delay=\"0\"][cmsms_quote image=\"136|http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Snapshot_20140820-300x225.jpg|medium\" name=\"Abhinav Bherav\" subtitle=\"Businessmen\"]\r\n<h3>Keep up the great work!</h3>\r\nThank you so much for your wonderful and professional dental care. My last dentist retired and I was nervous about selecting my future dental care professionals. After selecting Dental Clinic, I feel compelled to send you a note to let you know how great my experience was.\r\n\r\n[/cmsms_quote][cmsms_quote image=\"138|http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/IMG_20160107_220158_edit1_edit-226x300.jpg|medium\" name=\"Harsh Vardhan\" subtitle=\"Entrepreneur\"]\r\n<h3>Friendly staff, very helpful.</h3>\r\nOver the years my dentist has helped me overcome my fear of going to the dentist and fear of the pain. He is very patient, calming, takes time to explain things so I can understand them and has a sense of humor which helps me. I like my hygienist and the rest of my support staff.\r\n\r\n[/cmsms_quote][/cmsms_quotes][/cmsms_column][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/2\"][cmsms_heading type=\"h1\" font_family=\"Open+Sans:300,300italic,400,400italic,700,700italic\" font_weight=\"normal\" font_style=\"normal\" text_align=\"left\" margin_top=\"0\" margin_bottom=\"20\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Why Choose Us[/cmsms_heading][cmsms_heading type=\"h6\" font_family=\"Open+Sans:300,300italic,400,400italic,700,700italic\" font_size=\"14\" font_weight=\"normal\" font_style=\"normal\" text_align=\"left\" color=\"#07a7e3\" margin_top=\"0\" margin_bottom=\"20\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Let Us Help You[/cmsms_heading][cmsms_tabs mode=\"tab\" active=\"1\" animation_delay=\"0\"][cmsms_tab title=\"Kids Dentist\" icon=\"cmsms-icon-custom-brush-your-teeth\"]\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-144 alignleft\" src=\"http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img-2.png\" alt=\"img-2\" width=\"220\" height=\"220\" />Paediatric dentistry</h3>\r\nPediatric dentists are dedicated to the oral health of children from infancy through the teen years. They have the experience and qualifications to care for a child’s teeth, gums, and mouth throughout the various stages of childhood. Children are not just small adults. They are not always able to be patient and cooperative during a dental exam. Pediatric dentists know how to examine and treat children.\r\n\r\n[/cmsms_tab][cmsms_tab title=\"Oral surgery\" icon=\"cmsms-icon-custom-pin-tooth\"]\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-147 alignleft\" src=\"http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/img-1.png\" alt=\"img-1\" width=\"220\" height=\"220\" />Oral and maxillofacial surgery</h3>\r\nOral surgery deals with the treatment and ongoing management of irregularities and pathology of the jaw and mouth that require surgical intervention.Surgically removing teeth is the most common procedure that oral surgeons perform, but oral surgery as a specialty has a broad scope. This includes managing hard and soft tissue pathology, oral infections, dentoalveolar trauma and oro-facial pain and others.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/cmsms_tab][/cmsms_tabs][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_padding_bottom=\"50\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" data_bg_position=\"top center\" data_color=\"default\" data_padding_right=\"3\" data_padding_left=\"3\" data_width=\"boxed\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_width=\"boxed\" data_color=\"default\" data_bg_img=\"74|http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/content-dot3-1-14x300.jpg|medium\" data_bg_position=\"top left\" data_bg_repeat=\"repeat-x\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_padding_bottom=\"50\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][cmsms_heading type=