re to oral surgeries.[/cmsms_icon_list_item][/cmsms_icon_list_items][/cmsms_column][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/2\"][cmsms_gallery layout=\"slider\" image_size_slider=\"full\" slider_effect=\"slide\" slider_autoplay=\"true\" animation_delay=\"0\"]78|http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/restorativedentistry-150x150.jpg,94|http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/general-dentistry1-150x150.jpg,82|http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/teeth_1-150x150.jpg[/cmsms_gallery][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_padding_bottom=\"70\" data_padding_top=\"70\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat\" data_bg_position=\"top center\" data_bg_img=\"185|http://mysoresmile.tk/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/content-prlx-3-300x140.jpg|medium\" data_color=\"fifth\" data_width=\"boxed\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/4\"][cmsms_icon_box box_type=\"cmsms_icon_box_top\" title=\"Cosmetic Dentistry\" heading_type=\"h3\" box_icon_type=\"icon\" box_icon=\"cmsms-icon-custom-braces\" box_icon_size=\"40\" box_icon_space=\"70\" box_icon_border_width=\"0\" box_icon_border_radius=\"50%\" box_icon_color=\"#32dac0\" box_border_width=\"0\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Cosmetic dentistry is generally used to refer to any dental work that improves the appearance of a person\'s teeth.[/cmsms_icon_box][/cmsms_column][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/4\"][cmsms_icon_box box_type=\"cmsms_icon_box_top\" title=\"Dental Cleaning\" heading_type=\"h3\" box_icon_type=\"icon\" box_icon=\"cmsms-icon-custom-toothbrush\" box_icon_size=\"40\" box_icon_space=\"70\" box_icon_border_width=\"0\" box_icon_border_radius=\"50%\" box_icon_color=\"#32dac0\" box_border_width=\"0\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Teeth cleaning is part of oral hygiene and involves the removal of dental plaque from teeth with the intention of preventing cavities.[/cmsms_icon_box][/cmsms_column][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/4\"][cmsms_icon_box box_type=\"cmsms_icon_box_top\" title=\"Sedation Dentistry\" heading_type=\"h3\" box_icon_type=\"icon\" box_icon=\"cmsms-icon-custom-anesthesia\" box_icon_size=\"40\" box_icon_space=\"70\" box_icon_border_width=\"0\" box_icon_border_radius=\"50%\" box_icon_color=\"#32dac0\" box_border_width=\"0\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Sedation dentistry refers to the use of pharmacological agents to calm and relax a patient prior to and during a dental appointment.[/cmsms_icon_box][/cmsms_column][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/4\"][cmsms_icon_box box_type=\"cmsms_icon_box_top\" title=\"Complete Whitening\" heading_type=\"h3\" box_icon_type=\"icon\" box_icon=\"cmsms-icon-custom-braces\" box_icon_size=\"40\" box_icon_space=\"70\" box_icon_border_width=\"0\" box_icon_border_radius=\"50%\" box_icon_color=\"#32dac0\" box_icon_bg_color=\"#ffffff\" box_border_width=\"0\" animation_delay=\"0\"]A whitening transformation is a linear transformation that transforms a vector of random variables with a known covariance matrix.[/cmsms_icon_box][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_width=\"boxed\" data_color=\"default\" data_padding_top=\"70\" data_padding_bottom=\"70\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][cmsms_heading type=\"h1\" font_weight=\"normal\" font_style=\"normal\" text_align=\"center\" margin_top=\"0\" animation_delay=\"0\"]Make an Appointment[/cmsms_heading][cmsms_html]PHByYWN0bzphYnNfd2lkZ2V0IHdpZGdldD0iYTZiNjYwYTU1NTk0Yjg5MiI+PC9wcmFjdG86YWJzX3dpZGdldD4KPHNjcmlwdCBzcmM9Imh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LnByYWN0by5jb20vYnVuZGxlcy9wcmFjdG9wcmFjdG9hcHAvanMvYWJzX3dpZGdldF9oZWxwZXIuanMiPjwvc2NyaXB0Pg==[/cmsms_html][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_width=\"boxed\" data_color=\"default\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_padding_bottom=\"70\"][cmsms_column data_width=\"1/1\"][cmsms_contact_form form_plugin=\"cf7\" form_cf7=\"65{|}Booking Form\" animation_delay=\"0\"][/cmsms_column][/cmsms_row][cmsms_row data_padding_bottom=\"50\" data_padding_top=\"0\" data_bg_parallax_ratio=\"0.5\" data_bg_size=\"cover\" data_bg_attachment=\"scroll\" data_bg_repeat=\"no-repeat